Class ExportEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.katjahahn.parser.sections.edata.ExportEntry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    scala.Equals
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ExportNameEntry

    public class ExportEntry
extends java.lang.Object
implements scala.Equals
    Represents one entry of the export section.

    Is created by the export section instance and used for easy access to the export information without knowing the details of the internal structure.
